page.title: 10Language-Hemsworth Dialect
page.content: Dialect: As part of our language study we went out to ask people about local dialect.We asked if they knew what these local phrases meant. Owzeenoe ? How does he know ? Shutthigob! Be quiet! Thalaftagerranewun. you will have to get a new one. Ayampteeardnowt.I have not heard anything. Purremineer.Put them in here. Astorgorritwithy ? Do you have it with you ? Isthemumin ? Is your mum in ? Astagorritreight ? have you got it right ? Eezgooinooam. He is going home. Iamgorrit. I do not have it.
